Bismile ACK Non-Jndical Stamped Paper c: NOTA Stamp Vendor. AFFIDAVIT NOTARIAL NOTARIAL I, FATUBAI AHMED NASRULLAH wife of Late Ahmed E. Nasrullah aged about 78 years, by occupation domestic work, by religion Muslim, residing on 2nd floor, Khalil Mansion, Spence Road, Byculla, Bombay-400 008, do hereby solemnly declare as follows:- 1. That TAHER EBRAHIM KAS-UBHAI aged about 41 years is my nephew and the son of my brother Ebrahim Mohamedally Kasubhai and his mother is Sugrabai Ebrahim Kasubhai. 2.. That Taher was born at Bombay (Maharashtra) on the 15th day of September, in the year 1941. The above statements are true to the best of my knowledge. Solemnly affirmed at Bombay this 28th day of January 1983 } 33.0118 Gineara Identified & Explained by me. Before me. Deponent known to me. D. G PARANJPE ADVOCATE. NOTARY MONTERASHTRA STATE
